PrecisAppointment of DENIS E. SUTTON, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, WENDY E. DAWES, of Etobicoke, Ontario, and MAUREEN FLYNN, of Montreal, Quebec, as part-time members of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years, effective May 29, 2000.
